{
  "stem": "20609.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Being on a farm, I had rubber boots.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we decided to use the two boots as a water container, right?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So now I take the boots off and somebody goes out to-- to pour the water in them and they come back with the empty buckets and-- and the-- and the water, you know, for 50 people.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So we each got a zip of it, you know, like-- and it was the finest, taste like wine.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We were so thirsty.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You can imagine how, you know, we had-- you know, if you would have had a bucket, they would have let us pull up a bucket, right?",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So-- so four days later, we arrive in a place called Theresienstadt.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had never heard of a place in my life, you know.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And Theresienstadt was built many, many years ago as a fortress for Maria Teresa, the Austrian queen, therefore the name Theresienstadt, city-- city of Theresa.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it was-- it was built like a typical garrison city.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It had these big barracks which were not barracks in our sense of a way like we do in the United States Army.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "These were big buildings made out of-- build like brick and everything.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they used to house maybe 1,500 soldiers or something like that, you know.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Well, all of a sudden, we first get-- as we come in, we go into a reception area.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was a separate little camp.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "At that time, we were supposed to get the physical examination, you know, we're supposed to turn in our money and values and things like that, you know.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I didn't have-- I think I had, like, six kroner, which was like $0.40, on me.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "That's all I had.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
